Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, due to Perospero's ability,\Nthey have been coated with candy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Finally, just as Luffy and the \Nothers who got through the
