Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Candy Maiden...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Decoration!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Before the Dawn!\NPedro, the Captain of the Guardians!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can get through here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go around and get to the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, run straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.57,0:04:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Red Hawk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a flame?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pedro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.45,0:04:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dawn of the world will come before long!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His-{\i1}teia{\i0} ability is just like Luffy's!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wedding...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here she comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Luffy?!\NWe're surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Kick Katakuri off of the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.76,0:06:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll try to set sail somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This way!\N--Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!\NHe must've come through the mirror dimension!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen! Everyone has their own turn.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.11,0:06:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wedding cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna get involved with\NMama's Hunger Pangs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.88,0:07:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Armament Hardening!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.91,0:07:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Hawk Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! I'm using Haki but I can't hit him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper! Brook! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carrot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.97,0:08:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get shocked by the unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Luffy and his crew are...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the ones who our tribe
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Kozuki Family\Nhave been awaiting for centuries....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who'll lead the \Nworld to the new dawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For centuries?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:08:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Montd'Or, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Surround the southwest coast of the \NWhole Cake Island with battleships.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger, Big Bro Peros.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surround the coastline-{\i1}soir{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Straw Hat and the \Nothers are still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.27,0:09:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama was pursuing on land\Nand Katakuri-{\i1}sama{\i0} was waiting at the ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but are they still alive-{\i1}bon{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they're so persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.26,0:09:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tarte of Nuts Island, respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.86,0:09:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Amande on Nuts Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surround the southwest coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let Straw Hat and his clan get away\Nat any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coup de...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coup de Burst!\NThis ship can leap 1 km ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.39,0:10:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we try to set sail normally,\Nthe ship will be sunk by Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't quite understand\Nbut we can escape that way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's bet on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Mom is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carrot! You-{\i1}gara{\i0} go help them\Nget ready to sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?\N--Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wedding cake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Brook, Chopper!\NStay with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.07,0:10:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we can make it out of here,\Nit's meaningless if you guys end up dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We spotted the Straw Hats \Nat the southwest coast!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:11:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Minister Amande from \Nthe Tarte of Nuts Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.19,0:11:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll corner Straw Hat and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battleships are coming from the sea,\Nand Big Mom from the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.93,0:11:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're totally stuck in the middle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! We have to get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.73,0:11:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! But I have to load\Ntwo more barrels of cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do the rest so you go prepare\Nfor the Coup-de-something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll leave it to you then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:11:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Candy Wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Candy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.91,0:12:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! We can't use Coup de Burst like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.65,0:12:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is serious!\NThe Sunny has been caught by candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.39,0:12:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see the power of Candy Wave?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.81,0:12:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a perfectionist!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.84,0:12:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn Brook and Chopper back,\Nas well as the ship, candy jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:12:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing is done...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's either being destroyed by Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.16,0:13:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or being sunk by the cannons!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, you have no chance to survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beast Sword - Karajishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you know how much my bounty is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.08,0:14:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 700 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.24,0:14:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not someone who a weakling \Nlike you can defeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lick!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be the last time we talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:15:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You escaped death. Lick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pointless to die here!\NThe dawn of the new world is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.83,0:15:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.09,0:15:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll reduce it to 50 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.13,0:15:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on with your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you hadn't sacrificed your left eye,\Nyou would've been killed for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.34,0:15:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that how bad you wanted to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.44,0:15:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How old are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm 27...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've had 50 years of your lifespan drained\Nso it's like you've lived 77 years already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.37,0:15:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I wonder how many years\Nyou can expect to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I at least wanna choose where to die myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.66,0:16:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you were the captain of the Nox Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.26,0:16:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nox" means "night," doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.27,0:16:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds rather negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say, "Every night comes to an end."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,..."nox" means the same as...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,..."before the dawn"...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I can serve as a foundation for the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.26,0:16:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,new dawn of the world\Nthat the Master and the others are hoping for,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that's what I want the most.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think I have enough time for that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You once said that "before the dawn"\Nand "nox" meant the same thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the only thing that's waiting for you\Nis the eternal darkness called death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it comes! Gather up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the Roger Pirates' ship...\NThe Oro Jackson!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger! Oden-{\i1}sama{\i0}! Take me along!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do anything! Take me with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid, you still have to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a kid, I'm Pedro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.61,0:18:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My time is limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! Everyone has their own turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.66,0:18:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be patient and wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll come naturally. Your turn, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.50,0:18:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Pedro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pedro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.20,0:19:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say he died!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not gonna die!\NHe's the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.21,0:19:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got caught by the Navy\Nand at an execution ground in the East Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.30,0:20:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything this \Nworld has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the beginning.\NA new era has finally dawned.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.28,0:20:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wishes will be carried over.\NThe tide of time, people's dreams...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.34,0:20:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those things can't be stopped.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.16,0:20:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as people search for\Nthe meaning of freedom,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}those things will see no end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.60,0:21:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.36,0:21:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take... to sea, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you deny it,\Nthe dawn didn't come to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.41,0:21:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think... so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.87,0:21:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger said, "Everyone has their own turn"!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.25,0:21:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.94,0:21:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.72,0:21:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will break all of your-{\i1}gara \N\{\i0}Nmagic spells, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.02,0:21:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bombs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.15,0:21:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, you fool!\NWhat are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.44,0:22:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.82,0:22:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.28,0:22:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...had a feeling that this \Nwould be my last journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.26,0:22:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Pedro?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.68,0:22:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pedro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.46,0:22:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.28,0:22:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Pedro?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.78,0:22:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, you'll see how important it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.75,0:23:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to save Luffy and the others here\Nand let them set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.55,0:23:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pedro!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.43,0:23:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.98,0:23:15.08,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You-{\i0}gara{\i1} guys must go forward!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.36,0:23:27.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pedro cleared the path for \Na slight chance of escape!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:30.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, to crush that ray of hope,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:33.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Mom and Katakuri \Nmercilessly attack the Sunny!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.96,0:23:36.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is only one way to survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.09,0:23:40.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,With Pedro's wishes in mind,\NLuffy takes a big bet with determination!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.89,0:23:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"I'll Be Back! Luffy, Deadly Departure!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.72,0:23:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.84,0:23:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
